          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Retain Innovation and Manufacturing Excellence (RIME) Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Commerce to establish a pilot grant program to help eligible manufacturers retain retiring employees for up to 90 days&nbsp;for the purpose of&nbsp;transferring&nbsp;job-specific skills to other employees.</p>]]></text>
